## AGH {{ .Version }}

AGH is an agent operating system for running ACP-compatible coding agents as managed sessions.

### Installation

#### Homebrew
```bash
brew install compozy/compozy/agh
```

#### npm
```bash
npm install -g @compozy/agh
```

#### Go Install
```bash
go install github.com/compozy/agh@{{ .Tag }}
```

#### Verified Binary Installer
```bash
curl -fsSL https://agh.network/install.sh | sh
```

The installer downloads the release archive for macOS or Linux, uses local `cosign` when present or a
pinned temporary verifier when absent, verifies it against `checksums.txt`, installs `agh`, and
starts `agh install` when an interactive terminal is available.

#### Binary Download
Download the appropriate `agh_<os>_<arch>.tar.gz` asset for your platform and extract it.
